# BIgchainDB_Practice
https://www.bigchaindb.com/getstarted/

Install MongoDB and bigchaindb python package, steps from: https://docs.bigchaindb.com/projects/server/en/latest/quickstart.html


Issue while installation :
Command -  
vivek@ubuntu:~$ sudo apt-get install -y mongodb-org
E: Could not get lock /var/lib/dpkg/lock - open (11: Resource temporarily unavailable)
E: Unable to lock the administration directory (/var/lib/dpkg/), is another process using it?

Steps to resolve - 
vivek@ubuntu:~$ sudo rm /var/lib/apt/lists/lock



Hands on practice on examples from : https://docs.bigchaindb.com/projects/py-driver/en/latest/usage.html 
